Articles.Content:
So I had an unexpected crash during launch. It's a modded installation, and I'm hoping I can track down the source because these are my 'barebones' mods.

I'm running:

- Environmental Visual Enhancements

- Kerbal Engineer Redux

- PreciseNode

- RCS Build Aid

- Sensible Screenshot (+MagiCore)

- Kerbal Alarm Clock

- Waypoint Manager

 

All latest versions to the best of my knowledge.  A couple haven't been updated to 1.1.3 but appear fully functional.

Thing is I've had a couple crashes like this, and if consistent I'd like to track down a root cause if possible.  Error has occurred with completely different craft, and appears to happen while the game is doing some transitions from atmospheric to space flight (I was right on the 70km mark).  This crash not only stopped the game, it completely locked up my computer and forced me to reboot manually.
